        <title>Python便携版安装</title>
        <link>https://charles-7777.github.io/p/python%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%BA%E7%89%88%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 22:47:34 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://charles-7777.github.io/p/python%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%BA%E7%89%88%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.11.7/python-3.11.7-embed-amd64.zip&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.11.7/python-3.11.7-embed-amd64.zip&lt;/a&gt; 下载到D盘解压&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://bootstrap.pypa.io/pip/get-pip.py&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://bootstrap.pypa.io/pip/get-pip.py&lt;/a&gt; 下载到D:\python-3.11.7-embed-amd64&lt;br&gt;
将D:\python-3.11.7-embed-amd64 和 D:\python-3.11.7-embed-amd64\Scripts 添加到系统环境变量 &lt;br&gt;
python get-pip.py&lt;br&gt;
修改D:\python-3.11.7-embed-amd64\python311._pth文件，将import site前的#号去掉，即让其生效  不注释；
pip config debug&lt;br&gt;
创建D:\python-3.11.7-embed-amd64\pip.ini&lt;br&gt;
pip config set site.index-url &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;http://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
pip config set site.trusted-host mirrors.aliyun.com&lt;br&gt;
pip config debug&lt;br&gt;
python -m site&lt;br&gt;
pip config set site.cache-dir D:\PipCache&lt;br&gt;
pip cache info&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;pip 还可以暂时手动指定安装源
pip install open-webui &amp;ndash;no-cache-dir -i &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple&lt;/a&gt;
pip install open-webui -i &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
